OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening with plenty of sunshine. Clear
OL,7,Fskies overnight with a few mist and
OL,8,Ffog patches developing. Staying dry
OL,9,Fwith light winds and rather mild.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FAny early mist and fog soon
OL,12,Fclearing then another fine day with
OL,13,Fplenty of sunshine. Feeling warmer for
OL,14,Fall, especially in the north. Sea
OL,15,Fbreezes developing into the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
