OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith sunny spells on Monday. Cloudier
OL,7,Ffrom Tuesday with a some showers at
OL,8,Ftimes. Turning a little windier,
OL,9,Fespecially by Wednesday. Remaining
OL,10,Frather warm throughout.
